Objectives:

Apply textures to a model.
Understand the different kinds of textures.
Assignment Specifications:

Add at least 3 different texture maps to your Rat's Maze.
At least one texture must repeat several times over the polygon.  
At least one texture must use only the middle part of the polygon.  
At least one texture must exactly fill up the whole polygon.  
See StarterTextures2012.zip from our Notes page for help.
